    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jewish communities on high alert as Passover begins amid rising security threats nationwide</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Jewish communities face a heightened security threat this Passover, with NYPD Commissioner Jessica Tisch warning of an elevated alert as antisemitic attacks rise across the U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/02/jewish-communities-high-alert-passover-begins-amid-rising-security-threats-nationwide/"  >(Fox News)</a>
