        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russian military plane crash in Crimea kills 29 people</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Russian military transport plane crashed in annexed Crimea, killing 29 people aboard as officials pointed to a possible technical malfunction.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/russian-military-plane-crash-crimea-kills-29-people/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
