        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran's ceasefire push may be a 'cycle of deception,' analysts warn as shadowy figure gains power</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Iran&apos;s shadowy Ahmad Vahidi, a former Quds Force commander linked to deadly bombings abroad, is now more dominant than Iran&apos;s president or Khamenei&apos;s son, experts warn.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/irans-ceasefire-push-may-cycle-deception-analysts-warn-shadowy-figure-gains-power/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
