    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Turkey&#8217;s NATO role under scrutiny amid new report on Hamas, Muslim Brotherhood ties</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A new Foundation for Defense of Democracies report alleges Turkey under Erdogan has shifted toward Islamist movements, raising NATO alliance concerns ahead of a July summit in Ankara, Turkey.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/turkeys-nato-role-under-scrutiny-amid-new-report-hamas-muslim-brotherhood-ties/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
