    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran, proxy militias threaten US universities in Lebanon as Americans urged to flee now</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Iran and its proxy militias have threatened universities in Lebanon, U.S. officials say, and the State Department warned Americans to depart immediately.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/03/iran-proxy-militias-threaten-us-universities-lebanon-americans-urged-flee/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
