    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">A 12-hour drive through Iran offers glimpses of destruction, defiance and daily life</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A black banner hangs over the border crossing and portraits of Iran’s slain Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei stare down, promising vengeance against the United States and Israel.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/06/a-12-hour-drive-through-iran-offers-glimpses-of-destruction-defiance-and-daily-life/"  >(Bassem Mroue, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
