    <h3 itemprop="headline">After harsh winter, Ukrainians find joy in releasing bats rescued from war</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Children and volunteers gathered at a nature park on the edge of Kyiv to release bats into the night sky.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/06/after-harsh-winter-ukrainians-find-joy-in-releasing-bats-rescued-from-war/"  >(Derek Gatopoulos And Vasilisa Stepanenko, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
