    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Multi-agent AI is the new microservices</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      We just can’t seem to help ourselves. Our current infatuation with multi-agent systems risks mistaking a useful pattern for an inevitable future, just as we once did with microservices.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/06/multi-agent-ai-is-the-new-microservices/"  >(Info World)</a>
