        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Anthropic cuts OpenClaw access from Claude subscriptions, offers credits to ease transition</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Anthropic has blocked paid Claude subscribers from using the widely used open-source AI agent OpenClaw under their existing subscription plans, a move that took effect April 4 and has drawn pushback from subscribers who question both the cost implications and the company’s stated rationale.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/06/anthropic-cuts-openclaw-access-from-claude-subscriptions-offers-credits-to-ease-transition/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
