        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">U.S. and Iraqi officials say kidnapped journalist had been warned of threats</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      U.S. and Iraqi officials say U.S. journalist Shelly Kittleson, who was born and raised in Wisconsin, was warned of threats before she was kidnapped in Baghdad. They say she was told she might be abducted in the days before her abduction.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/01/shelly-kittleson-a-journalist-kidnapped-was-warned-of-threats-us-and-iraqi-officials-say/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
