    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump roasts Biden over autopen use in viral interaction with kids at White House Easter Egg Roll</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Trump turned the annual White House Easter Egg Roll into a comedy session, joking about selling his autographs and taking shots at President Biden&apos;s autopen use.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/06/trump-roasts-biden-over-autopen-use-viral-interaction-kids-white-house-easter-egg-roll/"  >(Fox News)</a>
