    <h3 itemprop="headline">GOP races to pass ICE, Border Patrol funding bill as priorities pile up, divisions emerge</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Donald Trump demanded Republicans pass a reconciliation bill by June 1 to fund ICE and border agents, bypassing Democrats who refuse to fund immigration operations.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/06/gop-races-pass-ice-border-patrol-funding-bill-priorities-pile-up-divisions-emerge/"  >(Fox News)</a>
