    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump administration terminates agreements to protect transgender students in several schools</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Education Department says it has terminated agreements that previous administrations reached with five school districts and a college aimed at upholding rights and protections for transgender students.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/06/trump-administration-terminates-agreements-to-protect-transgender-students-in-several-schools/"  >(Annie Ma, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
