    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AI-backed super PAC expands into multiple GOP primaries after claiming early wins</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Leading the Future, a pro-AI super PAC backed by tech executives, announced $1.5 million in spending to support three GOP candidates in key midterm primaries.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/06/ai-backed-super-pac-expands-multiple-gop-primaries-claiming-early-wins/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 06 Apr 2026 18:45:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 06 Apr 2026 18:45:00 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Deepa Shivaram, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/06/watch-npr-trump-iran-war-deadline-press-conference.webp" alt="Trump holds a press conference after profanity-laced post on Iran" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump holds a press conference after profanity-laced post on Iran</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Trump repeated threats to Iran during his Monday press conference, which he opened by describing the successful rescue mission for the downed airman over the weekend.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/06/watch-npr-trump-iran-war-deadline-press-conference/"  >(Deepa Shivaram, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
